    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet" />
    @* Asset keys MUST match the static-web-asset manifest exactly. With Blazor components hosted in
       an RCL, the keys are:
         - RCL assets:        _content/<RCL>/<path>
         - Host scoped CSS:   <HostProject>.styles.css   (named after the consuming web project,
                                                          NOT the RCL — see staticwebassets.build.endpoints.json)
       Using the wrong key makes @Assets[...] fall back to the literal key, which then 404s and
       leaves the page completely unstyled (login form, MudBlazor sizing rules, etc). *@
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="@Assets["_content/MudBlazor/MudBlazor.min.css"]" />
